name: Sophia Mitchell
description: I saw your profile on dating site. I liked it, and I would like more to recognize the you. My dear, I’m the girl and I’m 30 y.o, I would like to get acquainted with you if you are not against we can keep in touch with you. I’m sure I want to know you better. I’m writing you just for a serious intentions. I’m searching for a person with whom I can create strong and amicable family. What is your name? Where you live? Please,tell me about you as much as it possible, and I accordingly shall tell you about myself in my following letters. If you are the adult and a wise man, then I wait your answer. Write me as soon as you can, and I shall at once answer you for your letter without any problems. Also I apply on mine letter my photo, I hope you will like it. I hope you will write me and also will send me your photo. I shall look forward to hearing from you very much. Yours faithfully!
